@startuml Meetsendai_V0_DataCapture_Workflow
title Meetsendai V0 - Data Capture Workflow (EU Only)
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam wrapWidth 200

legend top right
  **Risk Levels (Transactions & Actor Swimlanes)**
  |<#White> White Box | Internal / Trusted Execution (Low Risk) |
  |<#E6F2FF> <color:black>Light Blue Lane</color> | Internal Trusted System Boundary |
  |<#Orange> Orange Box | PII Processing (Medium Risk) |
  |<#FFE6CC> <color:black>Light Orange Lane</color>| Auth / Transit (Medium Risk) |
  |<#Red> <color:white>Red Box</color> | External Data Ingress-Egress (High Risk) |
  |<#FFCCCC> <color:black>Light Red Lane</color>| Untrusted External Actors (High Risk) |
endlegend

|#FFCCCC|Sales Rep|
start
:Access Meetsendai Platform\n(HTTPS / TLS 1.3);

|#FFE6CC|Auth0|
:Authenticate User (Username / Password);
note right
  Auth0 only in V0.
  No SSO or Entra ID.
end note

|#E6F2FF|Azure Application (Docker) — EU Region|
:Issue Session Token (JWT)\nwith Signed Location Header (EU);
note right
  Location context is passed via
  signed application-layer headers.
  No external edge network (Cloudflare) in V0.
end note

|#FFCCCC|Sales Rep|
:Select Event in App;
:Capture Business Card (Photo)\n& Record Voice Note; <<#Red>>

|#E6F2FF|Azure Application (Docker) — EU Region|
:Receive Submission over HTTPS / TLS 1.3;
:Extract Signed Location Header → Confirm EU Context;

|#E6F2FF|Azure Application (Docker) — EU Region|
:Pass Image to OCR Engine; <<#Orange>>
:Pass Audio to OpenAI Whisper\nfor Transcription; <<#Orange>>
note right
  All processing occurs within
  EU Azure region (West / North Europe).
end note
:Fetch Tenant Product Docs from SQL DB;
:AI Cross-References Transcript\nvs Product Documentation; <<#Orange>>
:Generate Personalised Draft Email; <<#Orange>>
:Store Lead PII & Draft in EU Tenant SQL DB\n(TDE via Azure Key Vault, TLS 1.3 in transit); <<#Orange>>

|#FFCCCC|Sales Rep|
:Human-in-the-Loop:\nReview & Approve Draft Email;
:Dispatch Email to Lead; <<#Red>>

|#E6F2FF|Azure Application (Docker) — EU Region|
:Record Interaction Metrics\n(Scoped to Event / Tenant);
note right
  No cross-event aggregation or
  global statistics dashboard in V0.
end note

if (GDPR Data Subject Request?) then (Query / Delete)
    :Identify Subject Records in Tenant DB; <<#Orange>>
    :Execute Query or Full Deletion\nin EU Tenant SQL DB; <<#Orange>>
endif

stop
@enduml
